items.summary: Lots of people like this place

items.text: This place kill my wallet softly ;S
Using Citi M visa to get a discount in department store and 5% in Gourmet market.
Very big Department store in the middle of Bangkok. Have the Cineplex and Fitness Center.
shopping here is incredible for tourists, no tax and 7% vat refund- and naturally lower prices on similar goods from US/EU and more sales
Go to Vanila Brasseri
Epic food court, fantastic prices, massive choice. Cheat and get a table before you eat!
Best shopping center in BKK with the best brands and designers

เดียวนี้เหลือจอดฟรีแค่ 4 ชม. จาก 6 ชม. (ต้องมีบัตร Paragon Cineplex Card)
เงินไปเที่ยว เด๋วมันคงกลับ :p
